{
  "stem": "16.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had to dig ditches.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Here comes this prisoner-- a prison suit, but a German prisoner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had a black thing that's-- and nobody was fast enough for him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He just kept hitting you with, with, with that big rubber hose.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I said to myself, if I have to do this for the rest of my prison life, you know, I'm not going to survive even a week.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think I did that for, like, three days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I-- every evening, when I got back to my barracks, I just collapsed in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was so tired.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Finally, one morning, I see a group of German-- high-ranking Germans just talking to themselves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I took up enough courage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I walked up there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I started telling them in German that I have been assigned accidentally to a job that I'm really not-- one doesn't need skill for it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I am more skillful to work in the factory that I have been working all this time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was just a mistake that-- I must have caught him in a good mood.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because he said, all right, report to your-- to your previous man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Tell them that I said you are to work over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that's how I wound up back in my regular job, where I was reading on the door of the wagon, what's wrong with this, and what's wrong with that, and so on.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And this girl, that Polish girl, probably helped me toward saving my life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I tried to find her whereabouts after, after the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I just couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I didn't even-- didn't even remember her name, I'm sorry to say.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] these, these are-- these are things that, that saved my life, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
